sql:
SELECT AVG(session_duration) AS average_session_duration
FROM game_sessions
WHERE game_id = 123;

external_knowledge:
1 unit of time_spent is assumed to represent 1 minute in real time, hence 3000 units = 50 minutes; 
Extended game sessions refer to game sessions that last over 50 minutes; 
Highly engaged players are those who have played more than 5 extended sessions.

